'''“Microsoft Build 微軟開發者大會”'''是由[[微软|微软]]举行的一年一度的开发者大会,面向使用[[Windows|Windows]],,[[Microsoft_Azure|Microsoft Azure]]和其他微软技术的[[软件开发|软件开发]]人员和[[web开发人员|web开发人员]]。第一届大会在2011年举行,它继任了微软之前的开发者大会，[[Professional_Developers_Conference|Professional Developers Conference]](面向Windows操作系统的软件开发、[[MIX|MIX]]、[[web开发|web开发]]和微软技术如[[Silverlight|Silverlight]]和[[ASP.net|ASP.net]])。

==大會歷屆摘要==

===Build 2011===

Build2011于2011年9月13日至9月16日在[[阿纳海姆_(加利福尼亚州)|阿纳海姆 (加利福尼亚州)]]召开。这届大会主要侧重于[[Windows_8|Windows 8]],[[Windows_Server_2012|Windows Server 2012]]和[[Microsoft_Visual_Studio|Microsoft Visual Studio]]2012；它们的开发者预览版也在大会上发布。与会者还收到了一个运行Windows 8“开发者预览版”的[[三星集團|三星]][[平板电脑|平板电脑]]。

===Build 2012=== 
Build 2012于2012年10月30日至11月2日在雷德蒙德的微软校园举行,侧重于最近发布的Windows 8,[[Windows_Azure|Windows Azure]]和[[Windows_Phone_8|Windows Phone 8]]。与会者收到了附触控键盘的[[Surface_RT|Surface RT]]平板电脑,一部[[诺基亚Lumia_920|诺基亚Lumia 920]]智能手机,和100GB的免费[[OneDrive|OneDrive]](当时称为SkyDrive)存储。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.techsnapr.com/2012/10/31/build-attendees-get-surface-tablet-lumia-920-100gb-free-skydrive-storage/ |title=Build Conference 2012 Giveaway |access-date=2015-08-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170520024532/http://www.techsnapr.com/2012/10/31/build-attendees-get-surface-tablet-lumia-920-100gb-free-skydrive-storage/ |archive-date=2017-05-20 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>

===Build 2013===
Build 2013于2013年6月26日至6月28日在[[旧金山|旧金山]]Moscone中心举行。<ref>{{cite web|title=Announcing Build 2013|url=http://blogs.technet.com/b/microsoft_blog/archive/2013/03/26/announcing-build-2013.aspx|publisher=Microsoft|accessdate=26 March 2013|archive-date=2013-03-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130327195024/http://blogs.technet.com/b/microsoft_blog/archive/2013/03/26/announcing-build-2013.aspx|dead-url=no}}</ref>这届大会主要是发布Windows 8的Windows 8.1更新。<ref name=pcw-bluerevealed>{{cite web|title=Microsoft officially acknowledges Windows Blue|url=http://www.pcworld.com/article/2032104/microsoft-officially-acknowledges-windows-blue.html|publisher=PC World|accessdate=29 March 2013|archive-date=2015-09-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924130951/http://www.pcworld.com/article/2032104/microsoft-officially-acknowledges-windows-blue.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=ms-blueannounce>{{cite web|title=Windows Keeps Getting Better|url=http://blogs.windows.com/windows/b/bloggingwindows/archive/2013/05/14/windows-keeps-getting-better.aspx|publisher=Microsoft|accessdate=20 May 2013|archive-date=2013-05-17|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6Gg58b42D?url=http://blogs.windows.com/windows/b/bloggingwindows/archive/2013/05/14/windows-keeps-getting-better.aspx|dead-url=no}}</ref>每一个与会者都能收到一个[[Surface_Pro|Surface Pro]],附带[[蓝牙|蓝牙]]键盘的[[宏碁公司|宏碁公司]]Iconia W3(第一个8英寸Windows 8平板电脑),一年期限的Adobe Creative Cloud和100GB的存储[[OneDrive|OneDrive]](当时称为SkyDrive)。<ref>{{cite web|last=Weir|first=Andy|url=http://www.neowin.net/news/build-2013-attendees-get-free-8-inch-acer-iconia-w3-windows-8-tablet|title=BUILD 2013: Attendees get 8-in Acer Iconia W3 tablet [Update: ...and a Surface Pro!]|work=Neowin|publisher=Neowin, LLC|accessdate=26 June 2013|archive-date=2015-10-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151012023541/http://www.neowin.net/news/build-2013-attendees-get-free-8-inch-acer-iconia-w3-windows-8-tablet|dead-url=no}}</ref>

